      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <h3>üè† Local & Reliable</h3>
        <p>Fort Smith owned and operated. On time, every time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <h3>üõ†Ô∏è Expert Assembly</h3>
        <p>IKEA, Wayfair, Amazon - We assemble it all.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <h3>‚úÖ 100% Guarantee</h3>
